title: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: Description: An exception is thrown when trying to export data from the attached report.
OB: When trying to export data from a table containing highlight/map, an exception is thrown.
SR:
Steps to reproduce:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Navigate to a table that contains highlight/map.
3. Try to export the data from the table.
4. Observe the exception being thrown.
